  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ec9a774f1c3f94c5ab3b77c67ac7f734, type: 3}
  m_Name: LoopReflect_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ReflectBranch
  lines:
  - Man - I am never going to get used to dying.
  - But okay - I'm in a loop.
  - Is the universe helping me out?? Do I need to ask her to the dance to escape
    this loop?!?
  - But how???
  - Maybe if my confidence is high enough, I'll be able to get it out.
  - "Just need to figure out the right things to say\u2026."
  - This loop is just the universe's way of giving me practice runs. And when Daisy
    says yes to the dance, I'm free. Maybe.
  - I just need to build up my confidence enough to survive the drain of asking her
    to the dance.
  commitLines: []
